<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Zara McDermott has shared cryptic posts about 'hurting someone' and 'love winning' as rumours swirl following her split from Made In Chelsea's Sam Thompson.</p>

<p>The Love Island star, 23, took to Instagram stories to post two emotive quotes following claims she's in crisis talks with her ex about claims she's been unfaithful.</p>

<p>Her first said: 'Love always won in the end. No matter how it happened, no matter what it took, no matter what it meant. Fair or not, true or not. Love won.'</p>

<p>Drama: Zara McDermott has shared cryptic posts about 'hurting someone' and 'love winning' as rumours swirl following her split from Made In Chelsea's Sam Thompson</p>

<p>Adding a sad face emoji, Zara's second post then stated: 'We have all hurt someone tremendously, whether by intent or accident. We have all loved someone tremendously, whether by intent or accident. </p>

<p>'It is an intrinsic human trait, and a deep responsibility, I think, to be an organ and a blade. But, learning to forgive ourselves and others because we have not chosen wisely is what makes us most human. </p>

<p>'We make horrible mistakes, it's how we learn. We breathe love, it's how we learn, and it is inevitable.' </p>

<p>What are you saying? The Love Island star took to Instagram Stories to share an emotive quote hinting that 'love won'</p>

<p>Who have you hurt? She then shared a second quote about 'hurting someone' and 'making horrible mistakes' </p>

<p>Zara's posts come amid rumours that her explosive split from Sam will be played out in explosive scenes on an upcoming episode of Made In Chelsea.</p>

<p>A source told The Sun: 'The cameras have captured the whole fallout of Zara and Sam's dramatic split. It means viewers will get to see the raw emotion caused by Zara's infidelity last year, as Sam tries to come to terms with what has happened. </p>

<p>'There's going to be a lot of tears and rows as Zara fights for her relationship.'</p>

<p>MailOnline has contacted representatives for Zara and Sam for comment. </p>

<p>Drama: Zara and Sam's relationship has been 'hanging in the balance' after he learned she cheated on him while competing on The X Factor: Celebrity last year</p>

<p>Their broken relationship is now reportedly 'hanging in the balance' as the pair have been unable to talk, after Sam learned Zara had been unfaithful while competing on The X Factor: Celebrity last year.</p>

<p>Sam has been filming The Circle with pal Pete Wicks, but the Love Island star 'is fighting hard to get him back'.</p>

<p>Sam has taken some time away from Zara to film the The Circle, but that reportedly hasn't stopped her attempts to ask for forgiveness. </p>

<p>Desperate: Sam has taken some time away from Zara to film the The Circle, but that reportedly hasn't stopped her attempts to ask for forgiveness</p>

<p>An insider told The Sun: 'Their relationship is hanging in the balance. Sam left to film The Circle saying he couldn't be with Zara right now.</p>

<p>'She's fighting so hard to get him back. She's going to do everything she can to prove he can trust her again.</p>

<p>'Even though it's split them apart right now, people have got through worse in their relationships and gone on to be stronger, she loves him so much and isn't giving up hope that he'll forgive her. </p>

<p>'There are plans for them to meet up as soon as Sam is back. It'll be make or break for their relationship.'</p>

<p>Defiant: It's also been reported that Zara and Sam's split was filming by the Made In Chelsea cameras </p>
